Grandma,
what's happening?

1669
01:28:01,910 --> 01:28:03,176
Luke!

1670
01:28:09,051 --> 01:28:10,450
Uhh!

1671
01:28:10,452 --> 01:28:13,020
Uhh!

1672
01:28:13,022 --> 01:28:14,454
Hee hee hee hee!

1673
01:28:14,456 --> 01:28:17,291
Luke!

